<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<package xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/packaging/2010/07/nuspec.xsd">
  <metadata>
    <id>virtualdesktop</id>
    <title>VirtualDesktop</title>
    <version>1.21</version>
    <authors>Markus Scholtes</authors>
    <owners>zow</owners>
    <summary>C# command line tool to manage virtual desktops in Windows 10 and Windows 11</summary>
    <description>Command line tool to manage virtual desktops in Windows 10 and Windows 11.

Supports sequential command execution where results can be piped to subsequent commands. Features include:
- Create, remove, and switch between virtual desktops
- Move windows between desktops
- Pin applications/windows across all desktops
- Query desktop status and window locations
- Set desktop names and wallpapers (Windows 11)

Includes executables for Windows 10, Windows 11, Windows 11 24H2, Server 2016, and Server 2022.</description>
    <projectUrl>https://github.com/MScholtes/VirtualDesktop</projectUrl>
